data.description: Home Sweet Home!!! Don't miss this wonderful opportunity!!! A 2 story townhouse style condominium in a Gated Community. After you've explored this community and nearby ones, you will be amazed how perfect this home is. As you enter the house, you will enjoy the open floor plan with the full view to the family room from the kitchen, hardwood throughout the main floor, large living area, plenty of natural light, spacious bedrooms, private level backyard and many more. The excellent location of the community gives you all the conveniences to shopping, groceries, dining and schools. Easy access to I-85 and GA-316. Fabulous community pool for a perfect relaxation and enjoyment. This is a must-see!!!
